<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>The <link linkend="_class_risk_limits">RiskLimits</link> class represents the risk limits for a particular trading account. </para>



<para>The <link linkend="_class_risk_limits">RiskLimits</link> class provides methods to update the risk limits, set the log level, enable/disable the risk limits, check various risk conditions, and perform other operations related to risk management. </para>
</section>
